```

**Dropped from pbar:** `packages/domain` (CRM sample data only), `docs/`, `.github/workflows/ci.yml` (Neon-specific CI), `PLAN.md`, `solo.yml`, `to-fix.md`, `.planning/`.

**Kept and genericized:** `AGENTS.md` (stripped of CRM-specific content), `.pi/skills/` (project-local agent skills copied as-is).

